Final product goal:
The final product should support a full user flow where a user signs in, completes an onboarding questionnaire, connects Google Calendar, chooses which calendars to expose, syncs availability, receives personalized suggestions, manages their schedule through the platform, and later manages their profile settings including a profile image.

